presentation.fsa
Class GraphExporter

java.lang.Object
  presentation.fsa.GraphExporter

public class GraphExporter
extends java.lang.Object

This class is charged with exporting the current graph (or a selection of that graph) to one of four formats: LaTex-PSTricks, EPS, GIF and PNG. All of the methods are static; there is no need to instantiate to perform these functions.

Author:
Sarah-Jane Whittaker, Lenko Grigorov
